	* lwgeom/Makefile, lwgeom/lwgeom.sql.in, lwgeom/lwgeom_api.c,
	  lwgeom/lwgeom_inout.c, lwgeom/stringBuffer.c,
	  lwgeom/stringBuffer.h: Added a cstring(lwgeom) function that
	  returns WKT!

