2001-07-18 22:17  dblasby

	* postgis.h, postgis.sql.in, postgis_fn.c: Added function:
	  point_inside_circle(geometry, Px, Py, d)
	  - returns true if there is a point in geometry whose distance to
	  (Px,Py) is < d

